  },

   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "819a1917-842e-42ea-b149-045681d8a2cf",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Calculate the Pressure from the RDF"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 19,
   "id": "0a1f6cda-b7b2-4833-91f8-9e4887b2f7d9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "The excess pressure is = -26.1939 / (n k_B T)\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "rdf = np.copy(postproc.rdf.dataframe[\"H-H RDF\"].to_numpy())\n",
    "r = np.copy(postproc.rdf.dataframe[\"Distance\"].to_numpy())\n",
    "n_beta =  1.0 / ( postproc.parameters.total_num_density * postproc.therm.dataframe[\"Temperature\"].mean() * postproc.parameters.kB)\n",
    "pressure = postproc.therm.compute_pressure_from_rdf(r, rdf, 'Coulomb', postproc.potential.matrix)\n",
    "print('The excess pressure is = {:.4f} / (n k_B T)'.format(pressure*n_beta))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d3a52a69-7638-4233-bbc3-4e4ec1b98c2b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Dynamic Structure Factor"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 56,
   "id": "ecbe6021-7023-4253-9101-0cbf0fa60387",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "\n",
      "\n",
      "====================== Dynamic Structure Factor ====================== \n",
      "\n",
      "k wavevector information saved in: \n",
      " Simulations/OCP_cgs/PostProcessing/k_space_data/k_arrays.npz\n",
      "n(k,t) data saved in: \n",
      " Simulations/OCP_cgs/PostProcessing/k_space_data/nkt.h5\n",
      "Data saved in: \n",
      " Simulations/OCP_cgs/PostProcessing/DynamicStructureFactor/Production/DynamicStructureFactor_OCP_cgs.h5\n",
      "Data accessible at: self.k_list, self.k_counts, self.ka_values, self.frequencies, self.dataframe\n",
      "\n",
      "Frequency Space Parameters:\n",
      "\tNo. of slices = 4\n",
      "\tNo. dumps per slice = 12500\n",
      "\tFrequency step dw = 2 pi (no_slices * prod_dump_step)/(production_steps * dt)\n",
      "\tdw = 0.0126 w_p = 2.1057e+13 [Hz]\n",
      "\tMaximum Frequency w_max = 2 pi /(prod_dump_step * dt)\n",
      "\tw_max = 78.5487 w_p = 1.3161e+17 [Hz]\n",
      "\n",
      "\n",
      "Wavevector parameters:\n",
      "Smallest wavevector k_min = 2 pi / L = 3.9 / N^(1/3)\n",
      "k_min = 0.1809 / a_ws = 3.4252e+07 [1/cm]\n",
      "\n",
      "Angle averaging choice: principal_axis\n",
      "\tMaximum k harmonics = n_x, n_y, n_z = 55, 55, 55\n",
      "\tLargest wavector k_max = k_min * n_x\n",
      "\tk_max = 9.9505 / a_ws = 1.8839e+09 [1/cm]\n",
      "\n",
      "Total number of k values to calculate = 165\n",
      "No. of unique ka values to calculate = 55\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from sarkas.tools.observables import DynamicStructureFactor\n",
    "\n",
    "dsf = DynamicStructureFactor()\n",
    "dsf.max_ka_value = 10\n",
    "dsf.angle_averaging = 'principal_axis'\n",
    "dsf.no_slices = 4\n",
    "dsf.setup(postproc.parameters)\n",
    "dsf.pretty_print()"
   ]
  },
  {
